  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A JRPG with five classes that can be leveled up to 9999, over 100 dungeons, and expansive worldbuilding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world where people have become rare...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meanwhile, rumors are spreading that people are disappearing one by one at Mount Fuji,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and I have made up my mind to uncover the secret of Mount Fuji.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Class</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five classes: Shogun, Ninja, Archer, Mage, Younger sister</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Level: 9999</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time Progress(Active) battle: Thrilling real-time battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A battle where up to 5 characters can join the party</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Skills: Automatically acquired upon leveling up</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Life Skills: Fishing, Farming, ETC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Book: Choose desired skills to develop a unique character</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Party</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit a party to acquire all classes</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Legendary Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary items that can be acquired with a low probability</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Other</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual PvP, Ryokan(Automatic exp gain), Omikuji, Treasure, ETC</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fullscreen/Windowed mode: F4 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Default key: Arrow Keys, Enter, Esc, Mouse  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keybinding support </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ふじさんのぼり (Fujisan Nobori) means 'to climb Mount Fuji' in Japanese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start the adventure.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A JRPG with five classes that can be leveled up to 9999, over 100 dungeons, and expansive worldbuilding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world where people have become rare...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meanwhile, rumors are spreading that people are disappearing one by one at Mount Fuji,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and I have made up my mind to uncover the secret of Mount Fuji.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Class</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five classes: Shogun, Ninja, Archer, Mage, Younger sister</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Level: 9999</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time Progress(Active) battle: Thrilling real-time battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A battle where up to 5 characters can join the party</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Skills: Automatically acquired upon leveling up</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Life Skills: Fishing, Farming, ETC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Book: Choose desired skills to develop a unique character</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Party</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit a party to acquire all classes</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Legendary Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary items that can be acquired with a low probability</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Other</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual PvP, Ryokan(Automatic exp gain), Omikuji, Treasure, ETC</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fullscreen/Windowed mode: F4 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Default key: Arrow Keys, Enter, Esc, Mouse  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keybinding support </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ふじさんのぼり (Fujisan Nobori) means 'to climb Mount Fuji' in Japanese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start the adventure.</p>",
